-- Russia's MICEX falls below 1,400 points, lowest since mid-May
-- 
-- Mon Jul 21, 2014 05:11AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, July 21 (Reuters) - Russia's rouble-denominated MICEX index <.MCX> fell on Monday below 1,400 points for the first time since mid-May, with investors worried about the impact from sanctions imposed on several domestic companies and the conflict around Ukraine.

